About this item

  • LEADING BABYCARE BRAND: We know your babies require utmost care & protection while they grow. Your tot's skin is as soft as cotton and too sensitive to handle. Thus, it needs special care & attention every single moment.
  • BUMTUM PANT-STYLE DIAPERS: are uniquely curated to keep your baby's day & night full of comfort and materialized with cottony soft, breathable, and non-woven material that ensures a cosy experience.
  • COTTONY SOFT FABRIC:- Bumtum Diaper pants, fabricated with cottony soft material are soft & gentle on baby’s skin for regular usage. The top layer designed with a diamond pattern creates a larger absorbing area & uniformly spreads the liquid for easy & fast absorption.
  • LEAKPROOF:- There is nothing to worry about leakage with the double and bubble layer cuff used in the Bumtum diaper that snugly fits your baby without any discomfort. HIGH ABSORBENCY:- The large absorbing area of the pad ensures maximum dryness for the baby. It can hold up to 7 glasses of liquid, where 1 glass is equal to 50 ml.
  • EXTRA THIN CORE: It is designed to give Superior Absorbency and keep your Little Angel's skin Dry all day long. It is made with Ultra Soft Airfresh Material & a 360 Degree soft elastic band to keep your little one's delicate skin far from diaper rashes. The advanced double leak protection has made it the most preferred diaper pants.

neeraj Agnihotri
4.0 out of 5 stars An Excellent Blend of Quality and Affordability
Reviewed in India on 31 August 2023
Size: LargeUnit Count: 62.0Verified Purchase
I have been using the Bumtum Baby Diaper Pants in the large size for my little one, and I am thrilled to share that these diapers have exceeded my expectations in terms of both quality and affordability. This product has truly proven to be a gem that offers top-notch performance without straining the budget.

From the outset, the Bumtum Baby Diaper Pants impressed me with their thoughtful design. The large size fits my baby comfortably, and the elastic waistband ensures a snug yet gentle fit. The ease of putting them on and taking them off is a huge relief during busy diaper changes, making the process smooth and hassle-free.

One of the standout features of these diaper pants is their remarkable absorbency. They effectively keep my baby dry for extended periods, providing the kind of protection that's crucial for both my baby's comfort and my peace of mind. The technology used in these diapers deserves applause for its effectiveness in preventing leaks and ensuring a dry experience for my little one.

What truly sets the Bumtum Baby Diaper Pants apart is their affordability without compromising on quality. As a parent, I'm always on the lookout for products that offer the best value for money, and these diapers tick all the boxes. It's refreshing to find a diaper option that delivers premium performance at a price that doesn't break the bank.

Moreover, the attention to detail in the diaper's design is commendable. The softness of the material ensures that my baby's delicate skin remains irritation-free, even during extended usage. The diaper's breathable nature adds an extra layer of comfort, preventing any stuffiness or discomfort.

In terms of convenience, these diaper pants are a true lifesaver. The indicator that changes color when it's time for a change is a thoughtful addition, making it easy to know exactly when to switch diapers. This feature has saved me from unnecessary checks and has helped maintain my baby's hygiene effectively.
